            <p><strong>Morning:</strong> Use a light layer for a radiant base and environmental protection. Follow with sunscreen.<br>
            <strong>Night:</strong> Use a slightly more generous amount to support your skin's natural overnight repair cycle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rv-faq-item">
